@startuml
!theme cerulean
left to right direction
title UC-06 Manage XREF Dictionary\n(Agnostic Data Integration Middleware - Enterprise)

actor "Input Actors" as Input
actor "Business Analyst\n(Maker)" as BA
actor "Data Engineer\n(Maker)" as DE
actor "Approver / Checker" as Checker

actor "Output Actors" as Output
actor "System Operator" as OPS

rectangle "ADIM Middleware" as ADIM {

    usecase "Manage XREF Dictionary" as UC6
    usecase "Create XREF Entry" as UC61
    usecase "Edit XREF Entry" as UC62
    usecase "Deactivate XREF Entry" as UC63
    usecase "Search / View XREF" as UC64
    usecase "Approve / Reject Changes" as UC65
}

Input --> BA
Input --> DE

BA --> UC6
DE --> UC6
Checker --> UC65

UC6 ..> UC61 : <<include>>
UC6 ..> UC62 : <<include>>
UC6 ..> UC63 : <<include>>
UC6 ..> UC64 : <<include>>
UC6 ..> UC65 : <<extend>> "Production Environment"

OPS --> UC64

note right of UC6
  • Soft Delete (Deactivate)
  • Dependency Check
  • Maker-Checker Approval
  • Full Audit Trail
end note

@enduml